information: Force Ketten produces and supplies industrial chains from 2 mm to 16 mm for various applications and markets in Grade 100, Grade 80, Grade 50, Grade 30 and case-hardened quality segments for square and round steel chains. Stop, lashing chain, conveyor system, agriculture, lifting equipment, marine, mining, traction, forestry, DIY, slaughterhouses, plastic stop & lashing chain accessories, manure spreader, loading trolley, manure removal systems and all types of forged parts as well as sprockets (drive wheels) for all conveyor systems. These are the main products manufactured by Force Ketten Germany GmbH. Force Ketten Germany GmbH is a member of the EGINLIOGLU Group. The Eginlioglu Group is a market leader with over 15, 000 tonnes annual production in the welded steel sector.
